id: pm-qsk8
title: Deduplicate health and validate history-drift checks
description: "Duplicate audit 2026-05-22: jscpd found src/cli/commands/health.ts and src/cli/commands/validate.ts repeat the history drift scan and warning construction logic. Representative clones include health.ts:1202-1217 vs validate.ts:1190-1205 and health.ts:1219-1243 vs validate.ts:1206-1230. Search found closed implementation items pm-x0vj/pm-7vr9, but no active follow-up to single-source the check. Fix by extracting a shared history drift diagnostic builder that can render the compact health summary and the validate check payload from one scan result."
type: Chore
status: closed
priority: 2
tags[5]: code-quality,dedup,health,history,validate
