author: codex-duplication-audit
acceptance_criteria: Health and validate use one shared history-drift scan/diagnostic implementation; output differences are limited to format adapters; health and validate tests cover the shared warnings; pnpm build passes.
parent: pm-rnpb
resolution: Closed by extracting the shared history drift scan implementation.
expected_result: Health and validate reuse one history-drift diagnostic path while keeping command-specific output adapters.
actual_result: scanHistoryDrift was extracted to src/core/history/drift-scan.ts and health/validate now delegate to it via PR #54.
